{"title":"Cookie及Session使用","date":"2019-04-28T09:04:21.000Z","link":"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie","tags":["Java Web"],"categories":["Java Web"],"updated":"2019-10-14T06:46:34.269Z","content":"  <a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"会话技术的使用（Cookie）\">会话技术的使用（Cookie）<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#会话技术的使用（Cookie）\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"会话\">会话<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#会话\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li>一次会话：浏览器给服务器发送资源请求，建立会话，直到会话断开</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"功能：\">功能：<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#功能：\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li>在一次回话范围中的多次请求数据共享</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"方式\">方式<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#方式\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li>客户端会话技术（数据存在客户端）：cookie</li>\n<li>服务器会话技术（数据存在服务器端）session</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"客户端会话技术cookie\">客户端会话技术cookie<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#客户端会话技术cookie\"></a></h4><h5 id=\"入门\">入门<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#入门\"></a></h5><ol>\n<li><p>创建cookie对象</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Cookie(String name, String value)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>发送cookie对象</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">response.addCookie(Cookie cookie)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>获取cookie对象</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cookie[] cs = request.getCookies();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"comment\">//创建cookie对象</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     Cookie c = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Cookie(<span class=\"string\">\"msg\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"hello\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"comment\">//发送cookie对象</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     response.addCookie(c);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//获取cookie 对象数组</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     Cookie[] cs = request.getCookies();</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (cs != <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">         <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (Cookie c : cs)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">             String name = c.getName();</span><br><span class=\"line\">             String value = c.getValue();</span><br><span class=\"line\">             System.out.println(name + value);</span><br><span class=\"line\">         &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"原理\">原理<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#原理\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li>第一次设置中在响应头中添加 meg = hello</li>\n<li>第二次使用在请求头中添加  meg = hello</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"Cookie细节的处理\">Cookie细节的处理<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#Cookie细节的处理\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li><p>时候可以发送多个Cookie对象</p>\n<p>多次掉用addCookie就行</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>设置保存的时间</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>默认时，浏览器关闭后， 释放销毁</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>关闭后被保存时，设置持久化存储</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//1.positive 存到硬盘中</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//2.negative browser中的内存中</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//zero 删除 cookie信息</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">setMaxAge(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> seconds)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>保存中文问题</p>\n<p>tomcat8 以上可以添加中文数据</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>获取范围多大 能否共享</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>默认情况下不能共享</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>设置setPath到某个项目中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">setPath(String path)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//设置为/为根目录下的所有项目都能使用Cookie</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">setPath(<span class=\"string\">\"/\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>不同server之间的使用cookie 对象</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">setDomian(String path) :如果一级的域名相同，多个服务器之间可以共享</span><br><span class=\"line\">setDomain(<span class=\"string\">\".baidu.com\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"特点\">特点<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#特点\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li>放在浏览器中</li>\n<li>单个cookie的大小一般为4kb</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"作用\">作用<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#作用\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li>少用不太敏感的数据的</li>\n<li>在不登陆的时， 完成服务器对客户端身份的识别</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"案例的使用\">案例的使用<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#案例的使用\"></a></h4><h5 id=\"分析\">分析<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#分析\"></a></h5><ol>\n<li>有Cookie<ul>\n<li>响应数据， 欢迎回来</li>\n<li>写回Cookie对象</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>没有Cookie<ul>\n<li>响应数据， 首次访问</li>\n<li>写回Cookie对象</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h5 id=\"代码\">代码<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#代码\"></a></h5><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">response.setContentType(<span class=\"string\">\"text/html;charset=utf-8\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"comment\">//1.获取所有的Cookie</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">boolean</span> flag = <span class=\"keyword\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      Cookie[] cookies = request.getCookies();</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (cookies != <span class=\"keyword\">null</span> &amp;&amp; cookies.length &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (Cookie cookie : cookies)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">              String name = cookie.getName();</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">              <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"string\">\"lasttime\"</span>.equals(name))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                  <span class=\"comment\">// 存在 cookie</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                  flag = <span class=\"keyword\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">                  Date date = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Date();</span><br><span class=\"line\">                  SimpleDateFormat sdf = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> SimpleDateFormat(<span class=\"string\">\"yyyy年MM月dd日HH:mm:ss\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                  String ndate = sdf.format(date);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                  cookie.setValue(ndate);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                  cookie.setMaxAge(<span class=\"number\">60</span> * <span class=\"number\">60</span> * <span class=\"number\">24</span> * <span class=\"number\">30</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                  response.addCookie(cookie);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">                  <span class=\"comment\">//响应数据 获取cookievalue的时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                  String value = cookie.getValue();</span><br><span class=\"line\">                  response.getWriter().write(<span class=\"string\">\"welcome back  last visited\"</span> + value);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">                  <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">              &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (cookies == <span class=\"keyword\">null</span> || cookies.length ==<span class=\"number\">0</span> ||flag == <span class=\"keyword\">false</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          Date date = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Date();</span><br><span class=\"line\">          SimpleDateFormat sdf1 = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> SimpleDateFormat(<span class=\"string\">\"yyyy年MM月dd日HH:mm:ss\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">          String ndate = sdf1.format(date);</span><br><span class=\"line\">          Cookie cookie = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Cookie(<span class=\"string\">\"lasttime\"</span>, ndate);</span><br><span class=\"line\">          cookie.setValue(ndate);</span><br><span class=\"line\">          cookie.setMaxAge(<span class=\"number\">60</span> * <span class=\"number\">60</span> * <span class=\"number\">24</span> * <span class=\"number\">30</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">          response.addCookie(cookie);</span><br><span class=\"line\">          </span><br><span class=\"line\">          response.getWriter().write(<span class=\"string\">\"welcome to visit first\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//使用cookie技术</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//如果cookie 对象不存在的话， 那么我们就添加cookie对象 并设置时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 1.从response中获取cookie数组</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">两次request response 添加cookie对象 遗忘</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"jsp\">jsp<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#jsp\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie/1.png\" alt=\"1570843400761\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"session的使用\">session的使用<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#session的使用\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"概念\">概念<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#概念\"></a></h4><p>会话数据保存在server端的对象中就是http session</p>\n<h4 id=\"入门-1\">入门<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#入门-1\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li><p>获取session对象</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">    HttpSession session = request.getSession();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    session.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"hello\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\" welcome\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Object hello = session.getAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"hello\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">System.out.println(hello);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>使用Session对象</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">Object <span class=\"title\">getAttribute</span><span class=\"params\">(String name)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"params\">(String name Object obj)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">removeAttribute</span><span class=\"params\">(String name)</span></span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>原理分析</p>\n<p>确保在一次会话范围内获取的session对象是同一个</p>\n<p>session是基于cookie的</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>第一次获取session没有cookie 会在内存中创建Session对象 有唯一的ID 响应server  set — cookie JSessionID 保存id 再次通过cookie对象找到对应的session对象</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie/2.png\" alt=\"1570866798302\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"细节\">细节<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#细节\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li><p>客户端关闭后， 服务器不关， 获取的session是一个吗？</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>默认情况下</p>\n<p>不是客户端的会话结束 对应的Cookie头那么我们 session就不是一个</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>期望客户端关闭后保存session对象一致方法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cookie c = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> Cookie(<span class=\"string\">\"JSESSIONID\"</span>,session.getId());</span><br><span class=\"line\">c.setMaxAge(<span class=\"number\">60</span> * <span class=\"number\">60</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">response.addCookie(c);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>客户端不关闭，服务器的关闭后， 两次的Session一样吗？</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>默认情况下不一致 对象</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>对象不是同一个， 但是要求数据保存不丢失</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>session的钝化</p>\n<p>在服务器正常关闭之前， session对象序列化到硬盘上</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>session对象的活化</p>\n<p>在server启动之前将session文件从内存中转化为session对象</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>通过钝化 活化的方式保存信息值的相同</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>session的失效时间</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>session在server关闭时</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>使用invalidate</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>session的在30分钟内失效</p>\n<p>conf-&gt;web.xml文件中 设置session 对象的失效时间</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">session-config</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">session-timeout</span>&gt;</span> 30 <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">session-timeout</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">session-config</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"特点-1\">特点<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#特点-1\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li>用于存储一次会话的多次请求的数据， 存在server中</li>\n<li>session可以存储任意类型的数据，任意大小的数据</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"区别\">区别<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#区别\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li>session存储数据在server中 而cookie对象在客户端</li>\n<li>session没有大小限制， 而Cookie有</li>\n<li>session数据安全， cookie相对于不安全</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"session案例的使用\">session案例的使用<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie#session案例的使用\"></a></h4>","prev":{"title":"Servlet的基础使用","link":"2019/04/28/Java Web/Servlet"},"next":{"title":"IDEA配置javaweb项目","link":"2019/04/28/Java Web/Configuration of java web in IDEA"},"plink":"http://www.zqynn.cn/2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie/","copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://www.zqynn.cn/2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie/\" title=\"Cookie及Session使用\">http://www.zqynn.cn/2019/04/28/Java Web/sessioncookie/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}